headline.print_headline: Figure Skating: Russia's Lipnitskaia Beats Favorites to Win Gold
headline.main: Figure Skating: Russia's Lipnitskaia Beats Favorites to Win Gold

lead_paragraph: Julia Lipnitskaia's youthful exuberance shone out as the 15-year-old Russian trumped five-times gold medalist Carolina Kostner to win the women's title on her debut appearance at the European championships in Budapest on Friday.
